{
  "stem": "6924.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I decided to go to Zlotchov.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I came-- I came to Zlotchov.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I walked to Zlotchov, and I came there already when the German planes were bombing the town.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But when I came to my-- to my uncle, we still-- the Germans weren't there yet.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I stayed by my uncle, and the next day, the German came into Zlotchov.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I didn't realize who the Germans were.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The next day after they came, I-- in the afternoon, I walked out to the street seeing what's doing, and right away I was hauled away to the place where the Germans got all the Jews.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was in a jail, where they used to-- where they gathered all the Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they were killing them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was just a massacre.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "When I came to that place, I didn't realize what's-- what's-- what's what.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "When I came to that place, I saw already a big grave with all the hundreds of Jews laying in that grave.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they hauled me into that grave, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was in the grave also.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I realized--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Those people-- those people were already in the grave.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were dead.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were shooting all around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All around with machine guns, they were shooting those people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- when they pushed me into the grave, and I realized that I'm still alive, the first-- my reaction, I covered myself with two dead bodies and shooting continued.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And somehow, I felt-- I felt that people around me, but I felt that I'm still alive.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And at sundown, the shooting stopped.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And somehow I felt that I'm moving, that I'm alive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I pulled out from that grave, and everything was quiet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I got out slowly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was wounded by my foot, but I still could walk.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
